                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-457-18580405 t18580405-457-punishment-96"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">There were three similar indictments against the prisoner.</hi>
